00:54:47.370 --> 00:54:51.460
Margaret Anne who I like so much,
because the portrait that I drew.

00:54:51.460 --> 00:54:53.500
And you'll laugh if you read
the book, if you read Feel

00:54:53.500 --> 00:54:57.740
Like Going Home because it seems
so pale in light of the way

00:54:57.740 --> 00:54:59.630
